OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome sunny
OL,6,Fspells this evening. Becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy, with showers
OL,8,Fmoving in from the northwest. Showers
OL,9,Fmay merge into longer spells of rain
OL,10,Fovernight, becoming occasionally heavy
OL,11,Fwith a low risk of thunder.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA mixture of sunny spells and
OL,14,Fblustery showers on Tuesday, with a
OL,15,Frisk of hail and thunder. Feeling cool
OL,16,Ffor the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
